<h3>Safari at Udawalawe National Park</h3>
<p>A safari at Udawalawe National Park is a <strong>must-do activity in Sri Lanka</strong> for wildlife enthusiasts. Spot elephants, water buffalo, and exotic birds in their natural habitat.</p>

<h3>Whale Watching in Mirissa</h3>
